17 (B) In the case of a married couple filing jointly, each spouse who is otherwise
18 qualified for an exclusion allowed by this paragraph shall be individually entitled to
19 exclude retirement income received by that spouse up to the exclusion amount.
20 (C) The exclusions exclusion provided for in this paragraph shall not apply to or affect
21 and shall be in addition to those adjustments to net income provided for under any other
22 paragraph of this subsection;"
23 SECTION 2.
24 This Act shall become effective on July 1, 2025, and shall be applicable to all taxable years
25 beginning on or after January 1, 2026.
26 SECTION 3.
27 All laws and parts of laws in conflict with this Act are repealed.
